<p itemprop="description">A senior IT service manager leads complex service delivery activities and establishes best practices for service management across multiple services. They mentor junior service managers and drive strategic service improvements.</p>

<section class="role-details">
    <h2>Typical responsibilities</h2>
    <ul>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Lead complex service delivery initiatives across multiple services</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Establish service management best practices and standards</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Mentor and develop junior service managers</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Drive service innovation and digital transformation initiatives</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Lead strategic stakeholder relationships at senior level</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Support service portfolio management and investment decisions</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Collaborate with architects on service design and strategy</li>
    </ul>
</section>

